      "updated": 1783954902605,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Replication Factor\nDefine replication factor = n for replicating data across multiple nodes\nhow?\nSingle leader ( redis)\nMulti leader\nLeaderless ( cassandra)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Replication Factor\nDefine replication factor = n for replicating data across multiple nodes\nhow?\nSingle leader ( redis)\nMulti leader\nLeaderless ( cassandra)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hJasNDbBZMMs5AMU_-V-E",
      "type": "text",
