    {
      "id": "ZPpP9zymcTnCtUE7jRgcG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 533.5863524780405,
      "y": 3478.3079251647255,
      "width": 397.6796875,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1u",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 510815223,
      "version": 121,
      "versionNonce": 2008088005,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783955114505,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Anti-Entropy Repair\nWhat if replicas permanently drift apart?\n\nEntropy:\n\nEntropy means disorder.\nReplicas diverging:\nA ≠ B ≠ C\nis entropy.\n\nRepairing divergence:\nA = B = C\nis anti-entropy.\n\nThrough batch processing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Anti-Entropy Repair\nWhat if replicas permanently drift apart?\n\nEntropy:\n\nEntropy means disorder.\nReplicas diverging:\nA ≠ B ≠ C\nis entropy.\n\nRepairing divergence:\nA = B = C\nis anti-entropy.\n\nThrough batch processing",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Lc8mbWriqp7R78S8-Gs1c",
      "type": "text",
