    {
      "id": "neZ7x88aDSgS7tjApl_uC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3780.990682057175,
      "y": 657.7069265613933,
      "width": 487.2197265625,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1277364325,
      "version": 64,
      "versionNonce": 1563681285,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783954573520,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Redis Type | Internal Structure                   |\n| ---------- | ------------------------------------ |\n| String     | SDS (Simple Dynamic String)          |\n| Hash       | Listpack → Hash table                |\n| Set        | Intset → Hash table                  |\n| Sorted Set | Hash table + Skip List               |\n| List       | Quicklist (linked list of listpacks) |\n| Stream     | Radix Tree + Listpacks               |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Redis Type | Internal Structure                   |\n| ---------- | ------------------------------------ |\n| String     | SDS (Simple Dynamic String)          |\n| Hash       | Listpack → Hash table                |\n| Set        | Intset → Hash table                  |\n| Sorted Set | Hash table + Skip List               |\n| List       | Quicklist (linked list of listpacks) |\n| Stream     | Radix Tree + Listpacks               |\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0N2dkKNpX4NspS0hZQVfJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4717.082233372886,
      "y": 157.2232881763789,
      "width": 1323.9591064453125,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1119087499,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 907068619,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783954557636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Aspect                      | Redis                                        | Cassandra                                                |\n| --------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Primary storage             | RAM                                          | Disk                                                     |\n| Primary in-memory structure | Hash tables, skip lists, listpacks, etc.     | Memtable                                                 |\n| Durability                  | Optional (RDB/AOF)                           | Mandatory (Commit Log)                                   |\n| Disk format                 | RDB snapshots / AOF command logs             | Immutable SSTables                                       |\n| Read source                 | Memory only (normal operation)               | Memtable + SSTables                                      |\n| Background maintenance      | RDB snapshots, AOF rewrites                  | SSTable compaction, repair, cleanup                      |\n| Optimized for               | Microsecond latency and rich data structures | Massive write throughput and scalable persistent storage |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Aspect                      | Redis                                        | Cassandra                                                |\n| --------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Primary storage             | RAM                                          | Disk                                                     |\n| Primary in-memory structure | Hash tables, skip lists, listpacks, etc.     | Memtable                                                 |\n| Durability                  | Optional (RDB/AOF)                           | Mandatory (Commit Log)                                   |\n| Disk format                 | RDB snapshots / AOF command logs             | Immutable SSTables                                       |\n| Read source                 | Memory only (normal operation)               | Memtable + SSTables                                      |\n| Background maintenance      | RDB snapshots, AOF rewrites                  | SSTable compaction, repair, cleanup                      |\n| Optimized for               | Microsecond latency and rich data structures | Massive write throughput and scalable persistent storage |\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
