      "text": "| Scaling         | Move hash slots between masters | Rebalance token ranges\nautomatically       |",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Scaling         | Move hash slots between masters | Rebalance token ranges automatically       |",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YFywa-TZr84iIaku-E9UN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4635.966049573788,
      "y": 1203.4006317724118,
      "width": 782.939697265625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2g",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 836787845,
      "version": 56,
      "versionNonce": 1011758731,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783954851324,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Consistency     | Eventual by default             | Tunable (`ONE`, `QUORUM`,\n`ALL`, etc.)     |",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Consistency     | Eventual by default             | Tunable (`ONE`, `QUORUM`, `ALL`, etc.)     |",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KYsgSLW6RYesOAG3xao0T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4719.557315265411,
      "y": 499.48526111214767,
      "width": 954.6995849609375,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2h",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1378985573,
      "version": 97,
      "versionNonce": 725652773,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783954857844,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Feature         | Redis                           | Cassandra                                  |\n| --------------- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |\n| Architecture    | Master–Replica                  | Leaderless Peer-to-Peer                    |\n| Partitioning    | 16,384 hash slots               | Murmur3 token ring                         |\n| Hash Function   | CRC16                           | Murmur3                                    |\n| Shard ownership | Master owns slots               | Multiple replicas own token ranges         |\n| Replication     | Asynchronous leader-follower    | Leaderless, configurable consistency       |\n| Writes          | Sent to master                  | Sent to all replicas via coordinator       |\n| Reads           | Master or replica               | Any replica(s), based on consistency level |\n| Failover        | Promote replica to master       | Continue using surviving replicas          |\n| Scaling         | Move hash slots between masters | Rebalance token ranges automatically       |\n| Consistency     | Eventual by default             | Tunable (`ONE`, `QUORUM`, `ALL`, etc.)     |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Feature         | Redis                           | Cassandra                                  |\n| --------------- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |\n| Architecture    | Master–Replica                  | Leaderless Peer-to-Peer                    |\n| Partitioning    | 16,384 hash slots               | Murmur3 token ring                         |\n| Hash Function   | CRC16                           | Murmur3                                    |\n| Shard ownership | Master owns slots               | Multiple replicas own token ranges         |\n| Replication     | Asynchronous leader-follower    | Leaderless, configurable consistency       |\n| Writes          | Sent to master                  | Sent to all replicas via coordinator       |\n| Reads           | Master or replica               | Any replica(s), based on consistency level |\n| Failover        | Promote replica to master       | Continue using surviving replicas          |\n| Scaling         | Move hash slots between masters | Rebalance token ranges automatically       |\n| Consistency     | Eventual by default             | Tunable (`ONE`, `QUORUM`, `ALL`, etc.)     |\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
